brief_summary.textblock:
      The purpose of this study is:

        -  to evaluate if E4 has any effect on how the heart beats when a single dose is given at
           two different dose levels;

        -  to determine the ability to detect small changes in how the heart beats using a positive
           control: moxifloxacin, a quinolone antibiotic approved by the FDA as a positive control
           in thorough QT (TQT) studies;

        -  to assess the safety and tolerability of a single dose of E4 administered at two
           different dose levels;

        -  to measure the amount of study drug in the blood stream and how long it takes for the
           body to eliminate it (Pharmacokinetics) after administration.
